criteria.driver_alignment:
Discover — defined objective and explicit numeric assumptions (hurdle rate, initial cost, working capital, terminal value) that frame the cash flow projection;  
Implement — built a Python class to generate the year-by-year cash flow schedule and compute NPV/IRR;  
Reflect (and Validate) — inspected outputs, noted year-0 and year-10 bookends, ran sensitivity scenarios and used results to form a recommendation.
